Our Stock Market Recommendation System is designed to empower traders and investors with data-driven insights. It leverages advanced machine learning techniques and financial analysis to predict stock movements and recommend optimal trading decisions.

Features
Real-Time Analysis: Processes historical and live data for accurate forecasting.
Portfolio Optimization: Recommends stocks based on risk tolerance and investment goals.
User-Friendly Interface: Simple and intuitive design for seamless user experience.
Technology Stack
Programming Language: Python 3.10
Data Sources: Yahoo Finance, Quandl
Libraries:
Pandas, NumPy for data processing
TensorFlow, PyTorch for ML modeling
Matplotlib, Seaborn for visualization
How It Works
Data Ingestion: Collects historical and live stock data.
Feature Engineering: Processes data to extract meaningful indicators like RSI, MACD, and moving averages.
Model Training: Trains machine learning models on historical data.
Recommendations: Outputs buy, hold, or sell signals with confidence scores.
